{"id":"5f36a0e5fbf956000b716b65","typeName":"Pistol","category":"weapon","parentTypeChain":["Pistol","Weapon","CompoundItem","Item"],"handbook":{"categoryId":"5b5f792486f77447ed5636b3","price":7408},"common":{"name":{"zh":"柯尔特 M45A1 .45 ACP 手枪","en":"Colt M45A1 .45 ACP pistol"},"shortName":{"zh":"M45A1","en":"M45A1"},"description":{"zh":"MEU（SOC）手枪（“Marine Expeditionary Unit海军远征部队”；“Special Operations Capable特种作战能力”）正式命名为M45 MEUSOC，是一种弹匣式、后坐式、单动、半自动手枪，使用.45 ACP弹药。它是M1911的变种，自1985年以来一直是美国海军陆战队海军陆战队远征部队部队侦察分队的标准装备。\n\n改进的M45A1的特点是对原来的M1911A1设计进行了几处改动。一个特点是双后座力弹簧系统，通过降低后坐力的冲击峰值来分散.45 ACP弹的后坐力。它也有3点氚夜光瞄具，一个5英寸的国际竞赛枪管，左右手保险，皮卡汀尼导轨，沙棕色磨砂涂装。","en":"The MEU(SOC) pistol, (\"Marine Expeditionary Unit\"; \"Special Operations Capable\") officially designated the M45 MEUSOC, is a magazine-fed, recoil-operated, single-action, semiautomatic pistol chambered for the .45 ACP cartridge. It's a variant of the M1911, and has been the standard-issue side arm for the Force Recon Element of the United States Marine Corps' Marine Expeditionary Units since 1985. The improved M45A1 features several changes to the original M1911A1 design. One feature is the dual recoil spring system that spreads out the recoil force of the .45 ACP round by lowering the peak force of the recoil pulse. It also has 3-dot tritium night sights, a 5-inch national match barrel, ambidextrous safety, a picatinny rail, and a desert tan Cerakote finish."},"weight":0.205,"width":2,"height":1,"rarity":"Rare","backgroundColor":"black"},"properties":{"_raw":{"AdjustCollimatorsToTrajectory":false,"AimPlane":0.026,"AimSensitivity":0.65,"AllowFeed":true,"AllowJam":true,"AllowMisfire":true,"AllowOverheat":true,"AllowSlide":true,"AnimationVariantsNumber":0,"BackgroundColor":"black","BaseMalfunctionChance":0.2277,"BoltAction":false,"BurstShotsCount":3,"CameraSnap":6,"CameraToWeaponAngleSpeedRange":{"x":0.1,"y":0.2,"z":0},"CameraToWeaponAngleStep":0.1,"CanPutIntoDuringTheRaid":true,"CanQueueSecondShot":true,"CanRequireOnRagfair":f